Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨 下次要跟我约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这次跟说好的不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来还很期待着跟早苗阿姨一起去旅行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 别纠缠别人的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 约会的时候也会带上汐 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我也参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们三人好好玩一玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我排除在外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间还保持着你们结婚时的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一点也没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指那个布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐也很喜欢那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长的时间 真是对不起你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直把汐推给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能找到身为父亲的责任和义务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全都是靠了早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的把她培养成了一个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道该如何道谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.17,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下来模仿江川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.65,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 接下来我会靠自己来好好抚养她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她培养成和渚一样既为别人着想 又坚强的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生和我为了渚而换工作 也是在渚五岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用一生来报答这份恩情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就请你们幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会幸福的 跟汐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋说打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像条死鱼一样的家伙复活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话了 快投吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 好好记住你老爸的丑态哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐认为哪边会赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子可是看着我的英姿长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 看我怎么打败你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑至极
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得去道歉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没资格说别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起就再也没哭过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了 你当我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有了自己的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我必须要去养育汐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真太好了 没有迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了汐我们才有了寄托呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这下也终于结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长的时间真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我们是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次该你好好哭一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得撑不下去的时候 还有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你哭完之前 我都会在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 去叼了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也能听懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始就要跟爸爸一起住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做个乖孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我因为工作下班迟了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼儿园的接送还得拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 关于那边的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算最近就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的情况我从古河小姐那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还请多多关照了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 慢走 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那个人就是冈崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都干什么去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟古河家发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭纠纷？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以前的我肯定会发飙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我是冈崎 是冈崎汐的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一些原因 一直都把女儿托付给了妻子的娘家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起我们就要一起住了 还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 您太客气了 我们才是请你多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的孩子 跟小汐也很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要住在一起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一直以来劳烦您为我们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是会很辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一个人带大一个小孩子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的时期已经由早苗阿姨和大叔代为照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从今往后无论如何辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们的辛苦比起来 都算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么困难 随时可以来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司也会尽力帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 恕我冒昧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在是夏季保育中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小汐班级的班主任请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假是因为生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去参加保育士的研修会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来后 请重新和她打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的老师是个怎么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发长长的 既漂亮又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 爸爸要回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有外人来了 不可以开门的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事的话就给早苗阿姨打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话你会打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在天黑前回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两只手拿满了行李 帮我开一下门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从古河家拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子大家族和你的换洗衣服 还有玩具什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把这个放好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪里比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就放那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会做饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始会慢慢去学的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人一起学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子小姐 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好几年不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女儿 叫汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫芳野公子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子就是小渚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也一定能成为像小渚那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强又讨人喜欢的女性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前是妈妈的老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我听芳野先生说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您妹妹出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 虽然医生说这是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们一直都坚信着她会醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天是和妹妹一起出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打招呼 他们是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是您的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您妹妹真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小风 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我妹妹风子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位是冈崎先生和小汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了 我能抱她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你一说完就抱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小风 不能这样哦 太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 她就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冈崎先生同龄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为一直昏迷着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她本人的感觉还只是高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 感觉和汐没多大区别嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 姐姐和冈崎先生太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了 所以这孩子就是风子的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁乱也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是交到了新朋友真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 爸爸明天也请假了 我们一起出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喜欢团子大家族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是朋也君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老了很多啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直待在家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过你的母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一起去旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那北方的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你以前带我去过的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你过去很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起了很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该休息一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家乡去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的妈妈在那等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你牵着我的手 发誓要自己把我抚养成人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经足够努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家乡去 陪着你的母亲一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经… 可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经 完成了自己的使命了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是牺牲了自己的一切 养育我到今天了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我这样没出息的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗费了自己的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉地 我已经完成了自己的使命了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替换的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点不多的钱 我帮你放进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边就由我去联系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上别把行李弄丢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家的问题我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,债务问题也会妥善解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爷爷说拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就此告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多注意下身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒别喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟也别抽太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸又要出去了 你别吃太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要健康长寿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是让你那么寂寞 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会去报恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来后 好好给你做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 你也多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的一生是否是幸福的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最幸福的时候失去了爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后只剩下了父子两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我这个不懂得孝顺的儿子一直努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的人生 是否是幸福的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太耀眼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有客人来找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 你有什么会玩的游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 跟妈妈说我们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:23:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
